{"title":"Enfermedad Anticuerpos Antimembrana Basal (Anti-MBG)-2024-1","guid":"","filepath":"/Users/criaah/Vault/📚 Resources/Mapas-Mentales/Entidades clínicas/Reumatología/Enfermedad Anticuerpos Antimembrana Basal (Anti-MBG)-2024-1.smmx","root":{"id":"0","parent":"-1","text":"Enfermedad Anticuerpos\\NAntimembrana Basal (Anti-MBG)","guid":"5vlY_fnrcB-f_2jLThQMmw","children":[{"id":"1","parent":"0","text":"• Definición:","guid":"P_XNvqWuknFwFcjgvqYg8w","children":[{"id":"2","parent":"1","text":"Vasculitis capilares glomerulares/pulmonares","guid":"ncG7jzdvfmotFLgCpI1kDw","children":[]}]},{"id":"3","parent":"0","text":"• Anterior:","guid":"exM2rpou_im4jIXAage8wg","children":[{"id":"4","parent":"3","text":"Síndrome de Goodpasture","guid":"JdZfSxCpD9Zf9bK93wgbRg","children":[]}]},{"id":"5","parent":"0","text":"• Etiopatogenia: Depósito\\Nanti-MBG ➜ afectación basal","guid":"c_7cBa3VkufjHiNMMGoQuw","children":[{"id":"6","parent":"5","text":"• Renal: Glomerulonefritis, necrosis, semilunas","guid":"Jrbb4P6-YjH_Bo8jys-jKQ","children":[]},{"id":"7","parent":"5","text":"• Pulmonar: Hemorragia alveolar","guid":"CyE4nNI056A3RCRL1h1DcA","children":[]}]},{"id":"8","parent":"0","text":"Cuadro Clínico","guid":"lq_-w5OMkrjPc48E-DGFUw","children":[{"id":"9","parent":"8","text":"• Síntomas generales: malestar, fiebre, dolor articular","guid":"bMs4fktUdF4j_W2GVoeLCQ","children":[]},{"id":"10","parent":"8","text":"• Hemorragia alveolar: Difusa","guid":"6zKAfSjssQeQYcshdYnvCA","children":[]},{"id":"11","parent":"8","text":"• GN rápida progresión ➜ Enfermedades glomerulares","guid":"dR7hz8nlnkCKHj0GmOtskw","children":[]},{"id":"12","parent":"8","text":"• Intervalo síntomas renales/pulmonares: 1 semana - 1 año (30% casos)","guid":"6PMasG90c4mXF-oVHDPthg","children":[]},{"id":"13","parent":"8","text":"• Otros: náuseas, vómitos, diarrea","guid":"Lp4LAZeUVP_f_U_CRv2_oA","children":[]},{"id":"14","parent":"8","text":"• Curso: Brusco ➜ Insuf. respiratoria aguda + Insuf. renal","guid":"VptDrptQxg8ulRtsOsKb4A","children":[]},{"id":"15","parent":"8","text":"• Mortalidad: Hemorragia pulmonar + Insuf. respiratoria","guid":"bcCsk9SH0f30c5kta6wEng","children":[]},{"id":"16","parent":"8","text":"• Complicaciones crónicas: Insuf. renal crónica, fibrosis pulmonar, insuf. respiratoria crónica","guid":"dCydv0Oa9KVRgXeNUCy3cg","children":[]}]},{"id":"17","parent":"0","text":"Diagnóstico ","guid":"QSuwBBXNjFwHhfWeVp48GQ","children":[{"id":"18","parent":"17","text":"• Basado en: Cuadro clínico + Anticuerpos anti-MBG","guid":"JF7GkKzg79T7d_KYGjK7TA","children":[]},{"id":"19","parent":"17","text":"• Histopatología renal: Cambios típicos","guid":"xGGYYGhnMaa_XU1-A45jpw","children":[]},{"id":"20","parent":"17","text":"• Laboratorio:","guid":"AL2BQ7w85uX9ZS4KS_bM8w","children":[{"id":"21","parent":"20","text":"• ↑ VHS","guid":"oj8cNeB8PdAxVkYg-2CDHw","children":[]},{"id":"22","parent":"20","text":"• ↑ Proteína C-reactiva","guid":"fKqBFcqYUqppW3kG-niElQ","children":[]},{"id":"23","parent":"20","text":"• Anemia hipocrómica (normo/microcítica)","guid":"K4uZZDfQDbwv5N175TXG5A","children":[]},{"id":"24","parent":"20","text":"• Leucocitosis (eosinofilia posible)","guid":"aPBu2DRf_Q29K-ZH6GePHw","children":[]},{"id":"25","parent":"20","text":"• Rasgos de afectación renal","guid":"OuNvI9VuTyAmkg8GApiR0w","children":[]},{"id":"26","parent":"20","text":"• Imagen:","guid":"l4rEC9GwZdsF_olUUGMAMA","children":[{"id":"27","parent":"26","text":"• RX, TC alta resolución tórax ➜ Hemorragia alveolar","guid":"NkL72efjU5cqmFewg0S8og","children":[]},{"id":"28","parent":"26","text":"• LBA: Cambios hemorragia alveolar","guid":"kZP7_EJmnOB6PhQaK3dilQ","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"29","parent":"0","text":"Diagnóstico\\NDiferencial","guid":"QDKV2zHvwXZcAnw5fK1bOQ","children":[{"id":"30","parent":"29","text":"• Síndrome pulmón-riñón: Granulomatosis con poliangitis","guid":"v9RLMISYXZLEsoVSZvwBrA","children":[]},{"id":"31","parent":"29","text":"• Hemorragia alveolar difusa (no vasculitis)","guid":"u45EQk3lunC0YAhQTWO7eg","children":[]},{"id":"32","parent":"29","text":"• GN aguda: otras formas","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"33","parent":"29","text":"• Trombosis vena renal + embolia pulmonar","guid":"0RUyLlQJR21RhXcHrOlIZw","children":[]},{"id":"34","parent":"29","text":"• Insuficiencia cardíaca + renal","guid":"iEspF7Pfn3Q_KROhcwiTvw","children":[]}]},{"id":"35","parent":"0","text":"Tratamiento","guid":"YqjWLBjoUaJ2pTrOorEIMQ","children":[{"id":"36","parent":"35","text":"• Objetivo: Remisión","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"37","parent":"35","text":"Plasmaféresis","guid":"0FBXUOL0MC9MIrX8LV20BQ","children":[{"id":"38","parent":"37","text":"• Volumen: 4l plasma","guid":"WA_NF2ATDtsXYsw9yjG9OQ","children":[]},{"id":"39","parent":"37","text":"• Frecuencia: Diaria","guid":"NI9k8yoCDDbhddPL7-5uCw","children":[]},{"id":"40","parent":"37","text":"• Duración: Hasta desaparición anticuerpos anti-MBG (~14 días)","guid":"3KODcnC05DyvVplA4SFOtw","children":[]}]},{"id":"41","parent":"35","text":"1. Metilprednisolona","guid":"","children":[{"id":"42","parent":"41","text":"• Dosis: 7-15 mg/kg/d (máx. 1g/d)","guid":"_Px715PAIh59SwK9eorShg","children":[]},{"id":"43","parent":"41","text":"• Vía: IV, 3 días","guid":"IUqz_9SWFVcp0SW8_YvFpw","children":[]}]},{"id":"44","parent":"35","text":"2. Prednisona","guid":"","children":[{"id":"45","parent":"44","text":"• Inicio: VO 1 mg/kg/d (máx. 80 mg/d), 7 días","guid":"yNTVD1K3K9BLrrWX-5h0OQ","children":[]},{"id":"46","parent":"44","text":"• Reducción gradual:","guid":"pEoDlXf3m-ku4R6xeZ76ig","children":[{"id":"47","parent":"46","text":"• 8-10 semanas: 30 mg/d","guid":"aXFB1uQjI6_jO1lhDe6YGw","children":[]},{"id":"48","parent":"46","text":"• 15-16 semanas: 10 mg/d","guid":"ygq-g92WOg6s_cwegdNm8A","children":[]},{"id":"49","parent":"46","text":"• Posterior: 7,5-10 mg/d","guid":"7qVnJtA9Sqj6YZOEZFg3Qg","children":[]}]},{"id":"50","parent":"44","text":"• Duración: ~6 meses","guid":"UAq-mxeN-jdLeLE4wftgpA","children":[]}]},{"id":"51","parent":"35","text":"• Adicional: Ciclofosfamida","guid":"abibY36zgIliF-JTe8aVeA","children":[]},{"id":"52","parent":"35","text":"• Ciclofosfamida","guid":"yZcNStp0F31Ahdbe3MEH2g","children":[{"id":"53","parent":"52","text":"• Dosis: 2 mg/kg/d","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"54","parent":"52","text":"• Vía: VO o IV (si VO no posible)","guid":"b2aGbXEmKW_JoiwfPiUyQA","children":[]},{"id":"55","parent":"52","text":"• Duración: 2-3 meses","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"56","parent":"35","text":"• Inicio tratamiento: Inmediato post-diagnóstico","guid":"riEJCCJ79vFkdaAF1Fc_5A","children":[]},{"id":"57","parent":"35","text":"• Sospecha clínica: Glucocorticoide hasta confirmación anti-MBG","guid":"FRZ_gsiBFPIXIiTe-tKtig","children":[{"id":"58","parent":"57","text":"• Soporte agudo: Ventilación + hemodiálisis necesarias","guid":"uPwyPYoWpsgveeCSOsettw","children":[]}]},{"id":"59","parent":"35","text":"• Menos agresivo\\Nsi:","guid":"kdl4WhEbHweTIchSlRfgeA","children":[{"id":"60","parent":"59","text":"• Necesario tratamiento renal sustitutivo inicial","guid":"cQhOMU8Dat-oC0iHNoyB-g","children":[]},{"id":"61","parent":"59","text":"• Afectación total glomérulos renales","guid":"kXWUHLcUAmiYGuquEZo4Ww","children":[]},{"id":"62","parent":"59","text":"• Sin hemorragia pulmonar","guid":"-Al0LgWlVKH1VVFO6igLtw","children":[]},{"id":"63","parent":"59","text":"• Sin inmunosupresores a largo plazo","guid":"G2KLvqQtjt_ksCvhlp3mIA","children":[]}]},{"id":"64","parent":"35","text":"• Recurrencias: Tratar como primer brote","guid":"j612mmSHzwLpr7DyjeAv7g","children":[]},{"id":"65","parent":"35","text":"• Supervivencia post-tratamiento: 60-90% (fase aguda)","guid":"BYIbBawdZtQomu3dj0FvDQ","children":[]},{"id":"66","parent":"35","text":"• Riesgo alto si inicio con insuficiencia renal: 50% necesitan terapia renal crónica","guid":"oq4OtvbrO5WSZmmS4FAxYg","children":[]}]}]},"node_count":66,"relations":[],"cross_references":[],"specialty":"Reumatología","folder":"Entidades clínicas/Reumatología","